3 I is north east of U.
4 What is the relation of the agent I to the agent U?	upper-right	1
1 P and M are parallel, and P is under M.

1 G is placed in the left direction of V.

3 U is at the 12 o'clock position relative to T.
4 What is the relation of the agent U to the agent T?	above	1
1 L is on the left side and above P.
2 W is above and to the right of X.
3 K is to the upper left of L.
